<bibRefCitation author="Descarpentries" box="[819,1033,1132,1153]" pageId="3" pageNumber="84" pagination="129 - 132" refId="ref5721" refString="Descarpentries, A. 1981. Coleopteres Buprestidae nouveaux des petits Antilles. Revue Francaise d' Entomologie (N. S.) 3: 129 - 132." type="journal article" year="1981">Descarpentries (1981)</bibRefCitation>
