<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="85" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[173,660,733,967]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,296,866,887]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Remarks.</emphasis>
Originally described as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schaeffer" authorityYear="1905" box="[256,392,893,914]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Chrysobothris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="thoracica">
<emphasis box="[256,392,893,914]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">C. thoracica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Descarpentries" authorityYear="1981" box="[410,608,893,914]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Chrysobothris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guadeloupensis">
<emphasis box="[410,608,893,914]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">C. guadeloupensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was recently elevated to species rank by Woodley and Touroult (2012).
</paragraph>
